I use a pet. Suspend minion when moving, summoning pet when fighting - it´s all dps and easy to summon before engaging.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>It just seems too much hassle to reposition pets behind mobs so not to eat ripostes and rage, constantly watch for adds, all the things I gotta do to keep ole Jabober alive.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
Use Air pet for stuns and don´t worry about positioning on raids. Even when not positioned in the back it still does 50-60dps and all dps helps. As for enrage - /pet back off should do the trick. Use it when the mob is around 15% and it won´t get harmed too much. <br>
<br>
As for nuking: BoR and you can easily nuke twice per mob. <p>
